    "However, the training time of MPC-CA(FreeLB) is shorter than that of MPC-CA(PGD), which suggests that we could also choose FreeLB as the basic adversarial method if we pursue a shorter running time.",
    "Further details are listed in Table 10.",
    "Analysis of Training TimeTo further prove the effectiveness of our proposed MPC-CA model, we present the average training time in the four few-shot settings, as shown in Table 10 and Fig. 10.",
    "Additionally, the average training time of CRF-based is 2 h among all four minor lens settings.The results demonstrate that MPC-CA outperforms HCL-TAT in terms of F1 scores and compares favorably with HCL-TAT regarding training time, with even MPC-CA(FreeLB) running much faster than HCL-TAT.",
